<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;p&gt;</span>CineCopters have been gathering aerial stock footage for nearly 10 years.   There&#39;s very few places on the island of Ireland that we haven&#39;t shot variations of angles, lens sizes, light effects and times of year. <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;br&gt;</span>   We have everything from city scapes, rolling fields and crashing waves to land marks, government guildings and everything inbetween.  <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span> We have a set price for one or two clips purchased but if you need a number of clips we are more than happy to work out a deal and will always try and work within your budget. <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;</span>If you already know what clips you want please fill out the form below with the timecodes and we will be in touch with you within a few hours with your download link. <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;br&gt;</span> Timecodes are located at the bottom left of each video - minutes : seconds : (frames<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;small&gt;</span> - Not required<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;/small&gt;</span>).<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;/strong&gt;</span>  <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span>If you can&#39;t find what you&#39;re looking for or you&#39;re after something very spesific just <span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;a</span> <span style="color: #a6e22e">href=</span><span style="color: #e6db74">&quot;contact.php&quot;</span><span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&gt;</span>get in touch<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;/a&gt;</span> and we will be able to advise.<span style="color: rgb(231, 95, 85)">&lt;/p&gt;</span>

